, 182.3105, 183.6656, 183.3891, 183.162, 182.9846, 183.112, 183.2748, 183.576, 183.5085, 183.8344, 184.2232, 184.1808, 184.6696, 185.5189, 186.5864, 186.6061, 186.6699, 186.5382, 187.1511, 187.1472, 186.6985, 186.7074, 186.1398, 186.229, 186.5016, 185.5762, 186.3009, 186.2638, 186.8594, 186.2922, 186.6595, 187.4129, 187.2188, 187.3334, 187.5506, 187.8643, 187.835, 189.7298, 189.0024, 188.2663, 188.6388, 189.0472, 189.1987, 188.7641, 189.17, 189.5827, 189.9836, 189.5532, 189.8807, 189.8772, 189.9316, 190.6785, 190.6317, 191.5014, 192.3718, 191.0699, 191.7973, 192.5384, 192.1279, 192.4391, 192.7711, 192.2397, 191.1189, 192.6169, 192.4045, 192.9235, 192.307, 191.8674, 192.9526, 193.486, 194.0653, 194.1948, 194.9322, 193.2777, 193.8851, 193.8624, 194.1193, 194.6529, 194.8283, 193.9989, 194.5295, 196.2679, 196.7137, 196.9963, 196.9182, 197.03, 197.2606, 197.5242, 198.7512, 200.569, 200.5201, 199.9155, 199.9401, 201.3127, 200.9547, 200.4999, 198.9439, 198.7493, 198.4772, 200.0708, 199.1195, 199.2838, 200.0896, 199.3564, 198.0174, 198.7211, 198.2573, 199.4038, 199.8395, 199.8989, 199.0363, 197.2775, 196.5523, 196.8473, 195.259, 194.3776, 193.7393, 194.9694, 195.5674, 195.5484, 196.2043, 195.9147, 195.756, 196.3653, 197.3251, 197.7225, 199.378, 199.5263, 200.8949, 201.2894, 201.3974, 200.9628, 198.971, 199.7733, 198.567, 196.9726, 195.0492, 197.1852, 197.5674, 198.2757, 196.7394, 197.4598, 197.9721, 197.9073, 197.9028, 199.3689, 199.7837, 200.0023, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>单商品ETF基本面择时因子 | Sharpe 1.44 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告将基本面择时方法论通用化应用于商品期货。核心逻辑是：库存/仓单水平反映供给状态，当库存处于历史高分位（供给过剩）时做空，低分位（供给紧缺）时做多。报告以豆粕（原料大豆库存，Sharpe 2.1）、黄金（美债实际收益率，Sharpe 1.29）、煤炭（港口库存，Sharpe 1.07）三类品种为例，验证了基本面因子跨品种择时的可行性。</p>\n<p>复现中，我们将这一逻辑应用于全部80个商品期货品种，使用日频数据中的 <code>inventory_21</code>（库存21日口径）、<code>receipt</code>（仓单）、<code>profit</code>（利润）、<code>basis</code>（基差）等真实基本面字段，通过滚动分位数方法构建择时信号。最优变体为库存分位数因子（252天窗口），经时序标准化后Sharpe达1.44。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.07</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.02</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.2</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.51 / 0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.05</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.07</span></td><td>0.61</td><td>0.84</td><td>1.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.94</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.07</span></td><td>1.6</td><td>0.99</td><td>0.35</td><td>1.33</td><td>0.95</td><td>0.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>80.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>滚动分位数信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">P_t = \\frac{X_t - \\min_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s}{\\max_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s - \\min_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t = \\begin{cases} -1 &amp; \\text{if } P_t &gt; q_{\\text{upper}} \\text{ (高库存/高利润 → 看空)} \\\\ +1 &amp; \\text{if } P_t &lt; q_{\\text{lower}} \\text{ (低库存/低利润 → 看多)} \\\\ \\text{signal}_{t-1} &amp; \\text{otherwise (persistent)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">X_t</span> 为基本面指标值（inventory_21/receipt/profit/basis），<span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 为回看窗口（默认252天），<span class=\"math-tex\">q_{\\text{upper}}=0.90</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">q_{\\text{lower}}=0.10</span>。</p>\n<p>基差方向与库存/利润相反：高基差（backwardation） → 现货紧缺 → 做多。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe=1.19 (inv21_pctl_w252_q90_10_h10_raw)。库存因子(inv21/receipt)表现强劲，利润/基差单因子弱(Sharpe&lt;0.6)，变化率因子更弱(Sharpe&lt;0.3)</td><td>首轮实现全部8类因子(4个分位数单因子+2个变化率因子+2个组合)共16个变体</td><td>Sharpe 1.19, 5 个变体&gt;0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>诊断：TS ICIR=0.39, 71%品种IC&gt;0。inv21是最优因子。需要：(1)扩展inv21参数网格 (2)加_cs/_ts归一化 (3)加IC gate过滤弱品种</td><td>扩展inv21参数到7组+2组IC gate，加basis/combo变体。Pipeline自动启用_cs/_ts（共54变体）</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.19 → 1.44</strong>。h20+_ts为最优组合，ICIR升至0.57</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>尝试h15/h20等中间参数+inv21_rcpt_and组合</td><td>微调参数网格，新增inv21+receipt AND组合</td><td>Sharpe 1.36（未超R2），pipeline自动保留R2最优spec</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>：R1→R2 的归一化和hold_days优化。inventory_21用252天长窗口+20天持仓间隔+时序标准化(_ts)组合效果最好。时序标准化放大了波动率较大品种的仓位贡献，长hold降低了换手成本。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（58个品种有inventory_21数据，覆盖率约45%）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20日换仓（persistent信号，实际持仓更长）</li>\n<li><strong>信号特征</strong>: 低频交易，分位数极值触发，多空比例均衡（long 34%, short 37%, flat 29%）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - inventory_21数据非空率约45%，部分品种/时段缺失\n<p>- 年度Sharpe不均匀：2016年无数据，2020年较弱(0.13)，后半段(2021-2025)更强 - 与zhongxin库存因子相关性0.51，逻辑同源但数据字段不同(inventory_21 vs receipt) - _ts归一化放大了杠杆（年化波动率2.72），实际部署需控制杠杆</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.41s</li>\n</ul>"}